<p><a href="https://www.eurogamer.net/capcoms-pragmata-coming-2026-developer-promises">Next up is Pragmata</a>, the mysterious Capcom game that we've seen precious little of since its first reveal years ago. This time we got gameplay, loads of third person action goodness and a lovely sci-fi setting. Also, Diana is adorable. The game is set to come out at some point in 2026 to the PS5.
